metadata.name: The Lost Bid
metadata.description:
A Rememe Lab Complaint salute to the amazing @Hugofaz March 14th 2023 drop. 

The first 1st Meme Lab piece, 1st IRL The Memes performance art act, and first double-drop — a 1/1 auction + a bidder’s edition

Buy I didn't bid in time...sad times lol. But celebrate that its CC0.

Read up on the story of the original piece this is a rememe of..

(https://twitter.com/HugoFaz/status/1635653981820051458)
